                            All that piece and parcel of residential converted lands bearing Survey Nos. (i) 14/2 measuring 2 Acre 26 Guntas of Yalachanayakanapura Village, (Converted vide Official Memorandum No. 680346, dated 10.07.2024) (ii) Sy No. 75/4, measuring 17/½ Guntas, (Converted vide Official Memorandum No. 681938, dated 10.07.2024) (iii) Sy No. 75/6, measuring 2 Acre 05½ Guntas, (Converted vide Official Memorandum No. 644498, dated 03.04.2024) (iv) Sy No.75/7, measuring 17 ½ Guntas, (Converted vide Official Memorandum No. 644500, dated 03.04.2024) and (v) Survey No. 75/9, measuring 21 Guntas (Converted vide Official Memorandum No. 644499, dated 03.04.2024), totally measuring 3 Acres 21 ½ Guntas of Doddahulluru Village, Kasaba Hobli, Hosakote Taluk, Bangalore Rural District, , in all measuring 6 Acre 07½ Guntas RDPR E-Katha No.428, PID No. 150300401200521125 and commonly bounded on that:
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                        
                        <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!Booking__c.Project__c = 'Euphoria In The East'}">
                            All that piece and parcel of residential converted lands bearing (i) Sy. No-86/1, measuring 3 Acres 05 Guntas, (converted vide Official Memorandum No:406476, dated 29-12-2022), (ii) Sy. No-86/3, measuring 1 Acre 30 Guntas, (converted vide Official Memorandum No:406478, dated:28-10-2022) (iii) Sy. No-86/4, measuring 3 Acres 01 Guntas and 2 guntas Kharab , (converted vide Official Memorandum No:466479, dated:28-10-2022) situated at Doddagattiganabbe Village and residential converted lands bearing (iv) Sy. No-60/2, measuring 19-00 Guntas (Old No.60) (converted vide Official Memorandum No:406481, dated 28-10-2022), and (v) new Sy. No-61/4, measuring 8.00 Guntas, (Old No.61/2) (converted vide Official Memorandum No:406482, dated 28-10-2022), RDPR E-Katha PID No.150300401000520171, Situated at Pujena Agrahara Village, Kasaba Hobli, Hosakote Taluk, Bangalore Rural District, totally measuring 8 Acre 23 guntas and commonly bounded on that: 
                        </apex:outputPanel>
                        
                    </p>
                    
                    <p style="line-height: 1.5; font-size: 16px; text-align: left;">
                        <apex:outputPanel rendered="{!Booking__c.Project__c = 'Rhythm of Rain'}">
                            East by : Samethanahalli Soukhya Road<br/>
                            West by : Private Property<br/>
                            North by : Private Property<br/>
                            South by : Private Property
