                        </apex:outputPanel>
                    </p>
                    
                    <div style="text-align: center; font-weight: bold; font-size: 16px;">
                        <span style="border-bottom: 1px solid black;">SCHEDULE “B” PROPERTY</span>
                    </div>            
                    
                    <p style="line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify; font-size: 16px;">{!Booking__c.Undivided_Share_Of_Land__c} Sq.ft of undivided share right title and interest in Schedule A Property and Apartment No. {!Booking__c.Unit_NumberFor__c}, {!Booking__c.BHK_Type__c} in floor {!Booking__c.Floor__c}  
                        
                        
                         <apex:outputText rendered="{!Booking__c.Project__c == 'Rhythm of Rain'}">, Tower {!Booking__c.Block_Number__c}, Building {!Booking__c.Building_No__c}</apex:outputText> <apex:outputText rendered="{!Booking__c.Project__c == 'Whispering Petals'}">, {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Building__c}, {!Booking__c.Block_Name__c} </apex:outputText>  having carpet area {!Booking__c.Carpet_Area__c} Sq.ft and Balcony Area of {!Booking__c.Balcony_Area__c} Sq.ft,
                        
                        <apex:outputText rendered="{!Booking__c.Plot__r.Terrace_Area__c != null}">
                            terrace area {!Booking__c.Plot__r.Terrace_Area__c} Sq. ft.
                        </apex:outputText>                        
                        
                        and super built up area of {!Booking__c.Built_up_area__c} Sq.ft along with {!Booking__c.Parking__c} Parking slot in the building named a <b> “Sowparnika {!Booking__c.Project__c}”</b></p> 
                  
